casebody.data:
STATE of Missouri, Respondent,
v.
Terry M. ROBERTS, Jr., Appellant. WD 80394 Missouri Court of Appeals, Western District. ORDER FILED: OCTOBER 2, 2018 Julia E. Neidhardt, Jefferson City, MO, Counsel for Respondent. Jedd C. Scheider, Columbia, MO, Counsel for Appellant. Before Division Three: Anthony Rex Gabbert, Presiding Judge, Victor C. Howard, Judge, Alok Ahuja, Judge

ORDER

Per Curiam:

Terry M. Roberts, Jr., appeals from a judgment convicting him of the class B felony of assault in the first degree pursuant to Section 565.050, RSMo 2000. We affirm. Rule 30.25(b).
